<p>Town Hall closed so returned this<br/>E.H.B.</p>
<p>Centre for Soldiers Wives &amp; Mothers,<br/>31/12/15</p>
<p>Dear Mr. Layton,<br/>Could you assist Mrs. Langhorne who brings this note to you with a little money until her pay comes, she lives with another soldiers wife who has 4 children the youngest a fortnight old &amp; is unable to go out &amp; earn anything for either of them as she has been attended to the mother &amp; the house</p>
<p>Mrs. Bright is the other womans name, I enclose a note from Mr. Alex Sadler who knows the case</p>
<p>Yours truly<br/>E. H. Bennie</p>
